<html xnlns="http://www.w3.org/1999.xhtml">
<head>
<!-- $Id$ -->
<title>GridShib CA</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="@CSS_URL@" />
</head>
@HTML_HEADER@
<table id="index-table" width="100%">
<tr><td><p><p><p></td></tr>
<tr>
<td id="about-header" class="subheader" width="15%">About</td>
<td id="about-text" colspan=2>
<p class="about-text">
This is the GridShib-CA (version @PACKAGE_VERSION_STRING@). This software
allows you to acquire a short-lived (<1 day) Grid Credential through
your web browser and Shibboleth. After successfully authenticating, a
credential will be installed and is suitable for use with Grid Tools
such as GT4.
</p>
<p class="about-text">
Note that as with all Grid credentials this GridShib CA must be
trusted by any resources you use and the identity from the Credentials
(aka the Distinguished Name or DN) must be authorized (in the
grid-mapfile).
</p>
<p class="about-text">
For further documentation and the latest release please see 
<a href="http://gridshib.globus.org">http://gridshib.globus.org</a>.
Full documentation regarding this release can be found at
<a href="http://gridshib.globus.org/docs/@DOC_INSTALL_DIR@">
http://gridshib.globus.org/docs/@DOC_INSTALL_DIR@</a>
</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td id="prereq-header" class="subheader">Prerequisites</td>
<td id="prereq-text">
<p class="prereq-text">
Prior to using the GridShib CA on a new client system,
please <a href="checkPrerequisites.html">make sure you have the client
system properly configured</a>. Failing to do so may cause you
headaches as well as being insecure.
<p class="prereq-text">
To use the GridShib-CA you will need to be served by an identity
provider. If your home insitution does not provide an identity
provider included in the list blow, you can register with <a
href="http://www.protectnetwork.com">ProtectNetwork</a>, which is easy
to use and registration takes just a few minutes.
</p>
</td>
<td id="idp-logos" width="25%">
<a href="http://www.protectnetwork.com">
<img id="protectnetwork-img" src="protectnetwork.png" align="middle"
     alt="Protectnetwork.com"/>
</a>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td id="login-header" class="subheader" rowspan="4">Go</td>
<td class="login-idp" id="default-idp" colspan="2">
  <form action="@LOGIN_URL@">
    <p>
      <input type="submit" value="Click here to login and get credential"/>
    </p>
  </form>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="login-idp" id="idp-login">
<td colspan="2">
  <table width="100%">
    <tr>
      <td width="50%" align="center">
	<p>
	  <b>Login via ProtectNetwork</b>
	</p>
	<form action="https://@WWW_HOSTNAME@/Shibboleth.sso/WAYF/InCommon">
	  <p>
	    <input type="hidden" name="target"
		   value="https://@WWW_HOSTNAME@@SHIB_PROTECTED_CGI_BIN_URL@/login.cgi" />
	    <input type="hidden" name="providerId"
		   value="https://idp.protectnetwork.org/protectnetwork-idp" />
	    <input type="submit" value="Login via ProtectNetwork" />
	  </p>
	</form>
      </td>
      <td align="center">
	<form action="https://@WWW_HOSTNAME@/Shibboleth.sso/WAYF/InCommon">
	  <p>
	    <b>Login via Other Mechanisms</b>
	  </p>
	  <p>
	    Select your Identity Provider:<br/>
	    <select name="providerId">
	      <option value="urn:mace:incommon:uiuc.edu">U. of Illinois - Urbana-Champaign</option>
	    </select>
	    <input type="submit" value="Login" />
	    <input type="hidden" name="target"
		   value="https://@WWW_HOSTNAME@@SHIB_PROTECTED_CGI_BIN_URL@/login.cgi" />
	  </p>
	</form>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</td></tr>
<tr><td id="login-text" colspan="2">
  <p>
    After clicking on a link you will then be redirected back to that
    site to authenticate and then you will be returned to the GridShib CA.
    If you have any problems, please send email
    to <a href="mailto:gridshib-users@globus.org">gridshib-users@globus.org</a>
  </p>
</td></tr>
</table>
@HTML_FOOTER@
</html>
